all_answers.question: What attributes does the Rainsford show through the story
all_answers.subject: English
all_answers.text: Rainsford is an excellent hunter. He displays intelligence and resourcefulness throughout the story. He is also had good morals, shown when he refuses to hunt with Zaroff. He is a brave man as well, during the story, he doesn't give into feelings of panic or fear.
